Package: peaksat
Type: Package
Title: Peak saturation processing and analysis
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: person("Joseph R", "Boyd", email = "jrboyd@uvm.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package that coordinates the computationally instense task of processing bam files for peak saturation analsysis.  
    This process entails the iterative downsampling and peak calling using samtools and MACS2.  
    Visualization and analysis functions are also provided to interpret processing results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    ggplot2,
    data.table
Imports:
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
biocViews: Software, ChIPSeq, Sequencing, Visualization
